1
00:00:10,919 --> 00:00:11,359
This one.

2
00:00:18,280 --> 00:00:19,800
This one is for you.

3
00:00:36,399 --> 00:00:37,560
[When we got here,]

4
00:00:38,039 --> 00:00:38,740
[over 300 people]

5
00:00:38,740 --> 00:00:40,840
[had been slaughtered.]

6
00:00:41,359 --> 00:00:42,000
[The Xie family]

7
00:00:42,679 --> 00:00:43,679
[is too cruel.]

8
00:00:44,759 --> 00:00:45,920
[It's because of that]

9
00:00:46,280 --> 00:00:47,600
[secretly transported painting.]

10
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:16,359
[Brother,]

11
00:01:17,159 --> 00:01:18,120
[I will avenge you.]

12
00:01:19,099 --> 00:01:21,299
I will avenge you.

13
00:01:42,700 --> 00:01:43,980
It's Xie Huaiyun.

14
00:01:51,060 --> 00:01:52,040
Who's in there?

15
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:53,400
If you don't show up,

16
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:55,060
I'll kill

17
00:01:55,659 --> 00:01:56,700
your brother.

18
00:01:57,359 --> 00:01:58,560
You're so fast.

19
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,200
You should be thinking about

20
00:02:01,799 --> 00:02:03,879
how to get out of here.

21
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,519
Little slave,

22
00:02:08,319 --> 00:02:09,159
I bet you

23
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,680
dare to kill your master.

24
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,319
You crazy.

25
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:45,719
Xie Lingfeng.

26
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,280
Brother.

27
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,439
I'm just checking the private treasury.

28
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,400
Why do you bring so many people?

29
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:58,080
But I heard

30
00:02:58,780 --> 00:02:59,599
there are more than
one person inside.

31
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,039
If you don't believe me,

32
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:04,759
you can go in and check.

33
00:03:05,719 --> 00:03:07,159
But if you find

34
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,199
the room empty,

35
00:03:10,639 --> 00:03:11,400
how will you

36
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,919
compensate me for the disturbance

37
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,400
and the loss of face?

38
00:03:34,300 --> 00:03:34,900
Lady An,

39
00:03:35,620 --> 00:03:36,659
where have you been?

40
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:38,719
I...

41
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,080
I was painting inside the room.

42
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:41,659
Painting?

43
00:03:47,479 --> 00:03:48,400
What did you paint?

44
00:03:57,159 --> 00:03:58,039
I took the liberty

45
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,439
of sketching your portrait in my spare time.

46
00:04:01,319 --> 00:04:02,759
But my skills are poor,

47
00:04:03,319 --> 00:04:04,599
so I've never dared to show it.

48
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,719
You painted me?

49
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,020
Your grace and demeanor

50
00:04:13,639 --> 00:04:14,879
are unforgettable.

51
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:16,439
But a painting

52
00:04:16,879 --> 00:04:18,639
can never capture even a fraction of your true essence.

53
00:04:19,699 --> 00:04:20,360
I'll

54
00:04:21,139 --> 00:04:21,819
take the painting.

55
00:04:22,839 --> 00:04:24,040
It's been a long day.

56
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:25,480
Lady An,

57
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,120
you should get some rest.

58
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:42,839
Thankfully, you anticipated this.

59
00:04:43,399 --> 00:04:44,399
But can this painting

60
00:04:44,959 --> 00:04:46,079
truly convince him?

61
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:06,800
The threads have penetrated his bones.

62
00:05:07,319 --> 00:05:08,720
Ordinarily, he would have surrendered body and soul.

63
00:05:09,319 --> 00:05:11,439
Yet Xie Lingfeng still harbors rebellious intentions.

64
00:05:11,839 --> 00:05:12,800
He is undoubtedly a wolf in sheep's clothing.

65
00:05:13,199 --> 00:05:14,160
His prolonged presence is a grave danger.

66
00:05:28,199 --> 00:05:29,000
Go, go!

67
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:30,439
Hurry!

68
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,399
Go!

69
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:35,800
You too, you too!

70
00:05:36,399 --> 00:05:36,839
Go, go!

71
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:37,800
Go!

72
00:05:49,199 --> 00:05:50,480
The full moon isn't here yet.

73
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:52,240
Why?

74
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,279
This is the punishment

75
00:05:54,639 --> 00:05:56,199
for a regicide.

76
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,560
It will always be with you

77
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,519
until death.

78
00:06:52,959 --> 00:06:54,720
Then why did you save me?

79
00:06:59,199 --> 00:07:00,439
Because you turned back.

80
00:07:01,199 --> 00:07:02,040
Only those who turn back

81
00:07:03,199 --> 00:07:04,399
can taste the sweetness.

82
00:07:07,319 --> 00:07:08,399
This is a reward.

83
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,000
This is what a reward is.

84
00:07:25,079 --> 00:07:26,399
The feeling of being bitten by someone,

85
00:07:26,399 --> 00:07:27,180
isn't it unpleasant?

86
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,720
My lord,

87
00:07:30,399 --> 00:07:31,480
I can tell you

88
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,079
the location of the secret vault.

89
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,759
But the key...

90
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,759
It's up to you.

91
00:08:08,959 --> 00:08:09,560
Lady An,

92
00:08:10,139 --> 00:08:11,139
it's late at night.

93
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:12,399
Why are you here?

94
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:14,720
My lord,

95
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,199
I've just been promoted to the head of the painting department.

96
00:08:17,639 --> 00:08:19,360
I'm here to take inventory of the paintings.

97
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:20,879
I didn't expect

98
00:08:21,259 --> 00:08:22,139
the paths are so confusing,

99
00:08:22,579 --> 00:08:23,180
I got lost.

100
00:08:25,319 --> 00:08:27,360
I didn't realize this was...

101
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,240
Lost?

102
00:08:29,819 --> 00:08:31,540
Everyone in the Treasure Department knows

103
00:08:32,399 --> 00:08:34,200
this is a restricted area.

104
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:36,600
Unauthorized entry

105
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:40,159
is punishable by death.

106
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,039
Please understand,

107
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,759
I was unaware of this rule.

108
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,840
I'll leave right away.

109
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:47,639
Since you joined the Dept,

110
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,360
strange incidents have been frequent.

111
00:08:50,039 --> 00:08:50,720
Lady An,

112
00:08:52,559 --> 00:08:54,399
is it really just a coincidence?

113
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:02,679
What's wrong?

114
00:09:06,639 --> 00:09:07,679
It's my old illness.

115
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,120
Palpitations.

116
00:09:12,399 --> 00:09:13,320
My Lord,

117
00:09:14,039 --> 00:09:14,440
please...

118
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,120
help me.
